---
import '../styles/global.css';
import { House } from 'lucide-svelte';
import ThemeToggle from '../components/ThemeToggle.svelte';

const lastUpdated = "May 2, 2026";
---

<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/icon.png" />
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/icon.png" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Privacy — Peel</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Privacy policy for the Peel macOS app." />

		<!-- Prevent dark mode flash -->
		<script is:inline>
			const saved = localStorage.getItem('theme');
			const prefersDark = window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches;
			if (saved === 'dark' || (!saved && prefersDark)) {
				document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
			}
		</script>
	</head>
	<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
		<div class="fixed top-4 right-4 z-50">
			<ThemeToggle client:load />
		</div>

		<main class="flex-1 w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto px-8 pt-24 pb-16">
			<h1 class="scroll-m-20 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-balance">Privacy</h1>
			<p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm mt-2">Last updated {lastUpdated}.</p>

			<p class="text-muted-foreground text-xl mt-8">
				Peel does not collect personal data, does not use analytics or tracking, and does not transmit your files or tags. This page describes what data Peel handles and how.
			</p>

			<h2 class="scroll-m-20 border-b pb-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-12">Data stored on your device</h2>
			<p class="leading-7 mt-6">
				Tags, security-scoped bookmarks, and application preferences are stored locally on your Mac. They are not transmitted to Peel or any third party. Uninstalling the application removes Peel's data from your device.
			</p>

			<h2 class="scroll-m-20 border-b pb-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-12">Network connections</h2>
			<p class="leading-7 mt-6">
				Peel connects to the network only for the following purposes:
			</p>
			<ul class="my-6 ml-6 list-disc [&>li]:mt-2 leading-7">
				<li>
					<strong>Software updates</strong> (non–Mac App Store builds only). Peel periodically checks for new versions by fetching an update feed from <code class="bg-muted relative rounded px-[0.3rem] py-[0.2rem] font-mono text-sm">storage.douglaslassance.me</code>. The request includes only standard HTTP metadata such as your IP address and macOS version, and is not used for tracking.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>In-App Purchases</strong> (Mac App Store builds only). Purchases and receipt validation are handled by Apple's StoreKit framework. Peel does not see your payment information. Apple's <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" class="font-medium underline underline-offset-4">privacy policy</a> applies.
				</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="scroll-m-20 border-b pb-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-12">Files and folders</h2>
			<p class="leading-7 mt-6">
				Peel only reads files and folders that you explicitly grant access to via the macOS sandbox. Previews, waveforms, and tag suggestions are computed entirely on your Mac. No file content is uploaded.
			</p>

			<h2 class="scroll-m-20 border-b pb-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-12">Analytics and tracking</h2>
			<p class="leading-7 mt-6">
				Peel does not use analytics, telemetry, crash reporting, or advertising SDKs. No usage data is collected.
			</p>

			<h2 class="scroll-m-20 border-b pb-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-12">Children</h2>
			<p class="leading-7 mt-6">
				Peel is not directed at children under 13 and does not knowingly collect data from them.
			</p>

			<h2 class="scroll-m-20 border-b pb-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-12">Changes to this policy</h2>
			<p class="leading-7 mt-6">
				If this policy is updated, the revised version will be posted on this page with a new "Last updated" date.
			</p>

			<h2 class="scroll-m-20 border-b pb-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-12">Contact</h2>
			<p class="leading-7 mt-6">
				For questions or concerns, please contact <a href="mailto:peel@douglaslassance.me" class="font-medium underline underline-offset-4">peel@douglaslassance.me</a>.
			</p>
		</main>

		<footer class="p-8">
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
					© 2026 <a href="https://douglaslassance.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-foreground/30 hover:decoration-foreground transition-colors">Douglas Lassance</a>
				</p>
				<div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
					<a href="/" class="opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-200" aria-label="Home">
						<House size={20} strokeWidth={1.5} />
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
